{"tid":1533018,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【地下好硬】遭陶傑KO後唔忿氣 《環時》老總賴利君雅","createTime":"2019-09-02T15:58:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T22:56:51.000Z","uid":236171,"like":18,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"b4f2e18d57683a74fa2a6d6324dd066028e43501","tid":1533018,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:58:50.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n醬油：蘋果日報<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190902/60000174\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190902%2F60000174&d=7ie9SmB3qTQYrTFhvLfIgVCKRJWvDXkpEFRbHtszOvM%3D&h=5b306e29\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190902%2F60000174&h=a4a289d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190902/60000174</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">遭陶傑KO後唔忿氣 《環時》老總賴利君雅</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n7小時前<br />\n即時兩岸<br />\n<br />\n【新增動新聞】中共喉舌《環球時報》總編輯胡錫進昨日應邀，與香港時事評論員陶傑一同出席香港電台節目《視點31》的對談專訪。有觀看直播的網民事後認為，陶傑表現完勝對方。胡錫進今早在微博發長文，指主持利君雅與陶傑態度一致，自己是「二對一」，對談是打「逆風球」（逆境波）。<br />\n<br />\n胡在帖文開首，即指節目主持人是與陶傑態度一致的利君雅，這是他們的主場。他們與自己二對一。繼而又暗指利身為主持「不公平」：「真正了解這類對話的人都懂，重要的是主持人利君雅女士掌握着議題設置和決定由誰做每一個議題『最後陳述』的權力。」<br />\n<br />\n胡認為即使明知打「逆風球」，仍要出席對談。他說：「內地和香港輿論場之間有一道無形的屏障，很多時候我們這邊聲音很大，但過濾到那邊就變形了。他們那邊的聲音過濾到這邊也是一樣，這是雙方隔閡的重要原因。」<br />\n<br />\n胡又指，輿論溝通不應拿出一種「咄咄逼人的姿態」，自己不是為了與香港的受眾溝通，而是有別的「私心雜念」，將這場溝通當成自己對內地輿論場的某種「騷」。<br />\n<br />\n胡繼而再「埋怨」自己被不公平對待，「他們二人顯然存在對我『二打一』的默契，但這是我去香港電台演播室接受這種對話方式時就需要預期並且接受的，而且我覺得他們對這種優勢的利用比我之前想的要克制。」<br />\n<br />\n陶傑與胡錫進對談昨日過程在網上全程直播，胡指出，他支持香港和平示威者，惟斥責和平示威者「縱容」暴力行為「非常糟糕」，認為有損香港法治。二人就民間五大訴求各表己見。惟香港網民不少認為陶傑表現猶勝胡錫進，認為是「陶生贏晒」、「高下立見」。"},{"pid":"f7e4d9a42ae9dec7c3c38327a2ab74c7f9383a32","tid":1533018,"uid":287449,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:59:40.000Z","msg":"輸打贏要，正宗中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔意外<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCarry lam said that the China government fully support her and let her to handle the problem of Hong kong. She is lying. She cannot make any decision and cannot resign. One country two system? <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.co/eUo5Wkb6ga\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FeUo5Wkb6ga&d=7ie9SmB3qTQYrTFhvLfIgVCKRJWvDXkpEFRbHtszOvM%3D&h=38d41d2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.co/eUo5Wkb6ga</a>"},{"pid":"bd67a8e0971a55f80db7cac6639b4e7d0d61fb60","tid":1533018,"uid":35317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:59:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ffa1bcf96ee3742b657e7520e51d2746384697d","tid":1533018,"uid":72000,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f7e4d9a42ae9dec7c3c38327a2ab74c7f9383a32","tid":1533018,"uid":287449,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:59:40.000Z","msg":"輸打贏要，正宗中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔意外<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCarry lam said that the China government fully support her and let her to handle the problem of Hong kong. She is lying. She cannot make any decision and cannot resign. One country two system? <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.co/eUo5Wkb6ga\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2